Package projects.phonebook

Interface HashTable<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - The key type. It is IMPERATIVE that this is an immutable type!
    V - The value type. This can be any Object.
    public interface HashTable<K,V>

    HashTable is an abstraction over hash tables. Implementing classes should offer amortized constant insertion, search and deletion. The method names that you have to implement are the namesakes of Hashtable.
